sentences.english: Other agreements in 1880 and 1892 sealed the protectorate status of Bahrain to the British.

sentences.english: It was also presented to all those who later participated in the creation of the protectorates of Bohemia and Moravia.

sentences.english: Zanzibar became independent, after being a British Protectorate since 1890.
